---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title="Home" />
		<Sidebar/>
		<main>
			<div class="contentwrapper">
				<h1>Hi ❤️</h1>
				<p>
					Welcome to my humble home on the internet. I'm Alexandre Papin, a wannabe renaissance man from France. 
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Here you'll find a collection of thoughts I've forced myself to write down and share, hoping they'd get better in the process. 
				</p>
					
				<p>I hope you'll like them. If you do, let me know <a href="me@alexandrepapin.name">by mail</a> or on <a href="https://www.twitter.com/charmide">the twitter</a>. </p>
				<hr/>
				<h2>Recent musings</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/on/product-management">product management hats</a> - a long-winded attempt at theorizing the role.</li>
					<li><a href="/on/it-shouldnt-feel-hard">it shouldn't feel hard</a> - a reminder to myself that we tolerate too much, and also not enough.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>